# MancalaGamesCollectoin

MancalaFamily - collection of mancala games. Offline game.

Already implemented:
- Kalah
- Oware
- Congkak
- Dakon

Other settings to each of realised game:
- travel dirrection (standart, cross, clockwise, anticlockwise)
- scatter of pebbles (equable e.g. "4 4 4", random e.g. "3 2 7")
- attemps (many, one)
- cake mode (on, off)
- rotation Board for second player (on, off)
